            <description>
                <![CDATA[<h2>MG 高達維度爾</h2><p>MG 高達維度爾 ASW-G-XX Gundam Vidar，是屬於《機動戰士高達，鐵血的孤兒》第二季的機體，現已推出，立即為大家開箱看看。在動畫中，高達維度爾由蓋利歐·鮑德温（Gaelio Bauduin）駕駛，該角色採用「維度爾」作為化名，象徵北歐神話中的復仇之神。其原型為受損的高達基馬利斯（Gundam Kimaris Trooper），在月球外軌道聯合艦隊（Arianrhod Fleet）的改裝下，成為具備更高戰鬥力的機體。設計師形部一平參與了機體的監修，確保模型與動畫設定一致。</p><p><a title="_DSC9084" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218954/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218954_009b5c7253_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9084" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300228" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno-694x422.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="422" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno-694x422.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/gundam_vidar_by_inno.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1300229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/ezgif85b0a748dd7376.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="513" /></p><p>模型的高達框架有修改過，肩關節的活動範圍顯著提升，適合模擬動畫中的戰鬥姿勢。腳部的獵刃可展開，增加機動感的視覺效果，而膝部裝甲與推進器的同步移動確保了腿部彎曲時的流暢性與真實感。手槍的 blowback movement 是 MG 系列的可動機構設計，而步槍的彈匣可拆卸，允許玩家模擬裝填或更換彈藥的場景。突擊軍刀則配有可替換的刀刃零件，能重現動畫中脱離刀鞘的狀態，細節精緻。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9086" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270258/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270258_1ebb8acd4b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9086" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9088" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418161872/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418161872_b70934e9f6_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9088" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9087" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419024971/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419024971_34be9e8484_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9087" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9089" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218889/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218889_97e21b7cb4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9089" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9090" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414280/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414280_23230d9573_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9090" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9093" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418161852/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418161852_052d0e402b_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9093" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9094" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414265/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414265_84afff3025_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9094" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9095" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419024896/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419024896_cc9a54d34f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9095" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9096" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218834/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218834_5d34219373_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9096" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9085" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270228/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270228_0553df4234_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9085" width="1024" height="683" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="_DSC9097" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414255/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414255_0c06b1ce67_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9097" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9098" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218819/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218819_26f10320e4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9098" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9099" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218824/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218824_805cdb5b6d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9099" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9100" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270108/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270108_4ac8d3c142_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9100" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>駕駛艙的阿賴耶識 Type-E 特色系統，模型允許玩家選擇顯示啟動或關閉狀態，反映了機體在戰鬥中的不同模式。這一設計不僅增加了收藏價值，也讓玩家能更深入體驗動畫設定。除了武器與零件，模型還包括兩款蓋利歐·鮑德温的人偶，站姿與坐姿各一，適合用於駕駛艙內或獨立展示。</p><p>參考售價：6,600 日圓（含税）</p><h2>官方完成圖</h2><h2><a title="172481064359_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419233984/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419233984_b0b9945a61_b.jpg" alt="172481064359_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064478_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419039831/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419039831_162ed7d8ae_b.jpg" alt="172481064478_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064540_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419233959/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419233959_28dd86061c_b.jpg" alt="172481064540_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064651_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285508/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285508_1c165685a6_b.jpg" alt="172481064651_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064723_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418176772/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418176772_919551e02b_b.jpg" alt="172481064723_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064888_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285518/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285518_78e94ab6e6_b.jpg" alt="172481064888_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="172481064950_1200" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419285513/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419285513_13cb4bf76b_b.jpg" alt="172481064950_1200" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></h2><h2><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3 r-a8ghvy">HG 白騎士 Weissritter</span></span></h2><p>HG 機戰 OG 系列繼續有新作推出，今次是白騎士 Weissritter PTX-007-03C，隸屬 ATX 計畫，由艾克瑟蓮·白朗寧駕駛，以「亡靈 Mk-II・T 型」為基礎改造而成，專為遠程砲戰設計。它搭載特斯拉飛行裝置，實現人形姿態單獨飛行，機動性極高，但裝甲輕量化導致防禦力較弱，適合搭配南部響介的「古鐵」進行後方支援，亦是小編最愛之一的機體。武器包括威力強大的「騎槍重砲」、三連裝光束加農砲和電漿刀，戰術多樣化。</p><p><a title="_DSC9102" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414420/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414420_2803c31396_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9102" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9104" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270383/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270383_33da90eb0d_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9104" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9105" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270373/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270373_ebddea3430_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9105" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><a title="_DSC9107" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270338/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270338_5f0af1d89f_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9107" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9108" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419219054/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419219054_b918d6bbf0_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9108" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9109" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419219014/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419219014_c3c2837583_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9109" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>此 HG 模型依據動畫版大張正己風格設計，融入設計師齊藤和衞的原始設定，造型優雅且細節豐富。模型採用多軸關節，肩部、頸部和腰部靈活可動，能擺出雙手持槍的帥氣姿勢。配件包含騎槍重砲、三連裝光束加農砲、電漿刀、手掌零件及可動展示架，並附貼紙補色。白藍配色與透明綠雙眼零件還原經典形象，完成後高度約 15cm。</p><p><a title="_DSC9106" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54418162002/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54418162002_a6b86c21fa_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9106" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9110" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419218999/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419218999_dd662e0780_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9110" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9111" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419270348/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419270348_43997a9af2_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9111" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script><a title="_DSC9112" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54419414385/in/photostream/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54419414385_40de4f34f4_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9112" wi